{"id":638356,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/【朋友圈】任志强被北京市纪委留置谈话/","date":"2020-03-13T15:12:12Z","modified":"2020-03-13T15:55:04Z","title":"【朋友圈】任志强被北京市纪委留置谈话","content":"<p>CDT编者按：微信朋友圈，任志强的朋友发帖任志强失联。这两日网络有消息传出，任志强被北京市纪委“留置”，关押在北京市郊区蟒山市纪委培训中心。在其失联不久后，他的朋友在朋友圈发帖任志强失联。随后又有消息说，他只是被北京市纪委带走谈话。其原因是前不久他的写一篇文章《<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e4%bb%bb%e5%bf%97%e5%bc%ba%ef%bc%9a%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e7%9a%84%e7%94%9f%e5%91%bd%e8%a2%ab%e7%97%85%e6%af%92%e5%92%8c%e4%bd%93%e5%88%b6%e7%9a%84%e9%87%8d%e7%97%85%e5%85%b1%e5%90%8c%e4%bc%a4%e5%ae%b3/\">任志强：人民的生命被病毒和体制的重病共同伤害</a>》，在文章中，任志强批评了中共专制体制对疫情防治工作的破坏作用，并称习近平“是一位剥光了衣服也要坚持当皇帝的小丑”。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638361\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1086\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-5.jpg 442w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-5-138x300.jpg 138w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638369\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/2-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"490\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/2-8.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/2-8-300x294.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/2-8-768x753.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/2-8-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"GdT5A2I95Q\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e4%bb%bb%e5%bf%97%e5%bc%ba%ef%bc%9a%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e7%9a%84%e7%94%9f%e5%91%bd%e8%a2%ab%e7%97%85%e6%af%92%e5%92%8c%e4%bd%93%e5%88%b6%e7%9a%84%e9%87%8d%e7%97%85%e5%85%b1%e5%90%8c%e4%bc%a4%e5%ae%b3/\">任志强：人民的生命被病毒和体制的重病共同伤害</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《任志强：人民的生命被病毒和体制的重病共同伤害》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e4%bb%bb%e5%bf%97%e5%bc%ba%ef%bc%9a%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e7%9a%84%e7%94%9f%e5%91%bd%e8%a2%ab%e7%97%85%e6%af%92%e5%92%8c%e4%bd%93%e5%88%b6%e7%9a%84%e9%87%8d%e7%97%85%e5%85%b1%e5%90%8c%e4%bc%a4%e5%ae%b3/embed/#?secret=GdT5A2I95Q\" data-secret=\"GdT5A2I95Q\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"nGSE87d5vO\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e5%85%89%e4%bc%a0%e5%aa%92%ef%bd%9c%e9%bd%90%e6%88%88%ef%bc%9a%e5%8e%86%e5%8f%b2%e7%9a%84%e5%8f%b7%e8%a7%92-%e5%86%99%e5%9c%a8%e3%80%8a%e4%bb%bb%e5%bf%97%e5%bc%ba%e6%96%87%e7%ab%a0%e3%80%8b/\">光传媒｜齐戈：历史的号角 – 写在《任志强文章》之后</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《光传媒｜齐戈：历史的号角 – 写在《任志强文章》之后》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e5%85%89%e4%bc%a0%e5%aa%92%ef%bd%9c%e9%bd%90%e6%88%88%ef%bc%9a%e5%8e%86%e5%8f%b2%e7%9a%84%e5%8f%b7%e8%a7%92-%e5%86%99%e5%9c%a8%e3%80%8a%e4%bb%bb%e5%bf%97%e5%bc%ba%e6%96%87%e7%ab%a0%e3%80%8b/embed/#?secret=nGSE87d5vO\" data-secret=\"nGSE87d5vO\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><a class=\"st_tag internal_tag\" title=\"Posts tagged with CDS档案\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/cds%e6%a1%a3%e6%a1%88/\" rel=\"tag\">CDS档案 </a>| <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E4%BB%BB%E5%BF%97%E5%BC%BA\">任志强</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CDS档案 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E4%BA%B2%E8%87%AA%E6%8C%87%